Product Description

UGREEN 2021 Upgraded 36W Dual QC3.0 Metal Fast Car Charger Kit

Rapid charging & Smart Power

UGREEN USB car charger with advanced independent output technologies automatically identifies your device to provide a quick charge. When charging two devices simultaneously with this incredibly powerful 36W dual USB car charger adapter, each USB charging port will deliver exactly the right amount of power to match your device's need.

Safe and Reliable

UGREEN Fast Car Adapter kit fully complies with QC3.0 fast charge protocol and a built-in 56KΩ pull-up resistor. With upgraded intelligent chip with multi protections inside. UGREEN qc 3.0 car charger adapter provides reliable conductivity and stable charging current, protecting your smartphones from damage due to over-current or over-voltage. Multi-protect safety system and premium grade circuitry completely protect you and your devices.

Premium material

UGREEN upgraded metal cigarette lighter will not be burnt-out, which is safer than a plastic one. The Type C charging cable's unique aluminum alloy case with a reinforced connector has a 10000+ lifespan based on plugging and unplugging test.

Safe Protection

Our unique Safety System protects against shorts, surges, and other dangers to keep you and your devices safe.

Fearless bumps

Don’t be afraid of bumps even when driving on rough roads. Spring contact design can ensure the stability of the charger.

Fast heat dissipation

Premium aluminum shell design allows the charger to quickly dissipate heat, ensuring the safety of you and your devices.
